# --- [ DESCRIPTION ] ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#%   A '.gitignore' file specifies intentionally untracked files that Git should ignore        %#
#%   It helps ensure sensitive or irrelevant files (state, caches, etc.) are not committed.    %#
#%                                                                                             %#
#% ADDITIONAL INFORMATION                                                                      %#
#%   Official Git Documentation: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore                            %#
#%   This file uses an allowlist pattern: deny everything (**), then explicitly include        %#
#%   only the files and directories that belong in the repository.                             %#
#%                                                                                             %#
#%                                                                                             %#
# --- [ IMPLEMENTATION ] ---------------------------------------------------------------------- #
